{"tid":1962342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情已經受控,聽日武漢開城啦佢老母！","createTime":"2020-04-07T11:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T12:06:27.000Z","uid":272686,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96e2be2aef25579a5dbdde09830826ba28e62d44","tid":1962342,"uid":272686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:55:52.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1242220/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%A7%A3%E5%B0%81%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B3-%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E9%80%BE5-5%E8%90%AC%E5%90%8D%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E4%B9%98%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A%E9%9B%A2%E6%BC%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1242220%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%258D%25B3-%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2588%25E9%2580%25BE5-5%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25B9%2598%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25BC%25A2&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=ef54f10b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1242220%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%25B0%2581%25E5%259C%25A8%25E5%258D%25B3-%25E9%25A0%2590%25E8%25A8%2588%25E9%2580%25BE5-5%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25B9%2598%25E7%2581%25AB%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%259B%25A2%25E6%25BC%25A2&h=d11c00e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1242220/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%A7%A3%E5%B0%81%E5%9C%A8%E5%8D%B3-%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%88%E9%80%BE5-5%E8%90%AC%E5%90%8D%E6%97%85%E5%AE%A2%E4%B9%98%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A%E9%9B%A2%E6%BC%A2</a><br />\n<br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n武漢解封在即 預計逾5.5萬名旅客乘火車離漢<br />\n 2020-04-07 18:13中國<br />\n     <br />\n<br />\n 武漢市即將解封，武漢鐵路工作人員連日來忙碌在工作崗位上，為4月8日列車開行做準備。(新華社圖片)<br />\n武漢市即將解封，武漢鐵路工作人員連日來忙碌在工作崗位上，為4月8日列車開行做準備。(新華社圖片)<br />\n中國鐵路武漢局，根據湖北省新冠肺炎疫情防控指揮部通告，從午夜12時起（4月8日零時）起，武漢市解除離漢離鄂通道管控措施，有序恢復對外交通，離漢人員憑湖北健康碼「綠碼」安全有序流動。為此，武漢地區武昌站、武漢站、漢口站等火車站將重新開啟進站通道，恢復辦理旅客進站客運業務，旅客持健康碼「綠碼」經測量體溫、身份核驗後可乘車出行。<br />\n<br />\n中國鐵路武漢局集團公司相關部門負責人表示，按照屬地防疫部門和國鐵集團的要求，武漢鐵路部門精心做好進站通道恢復前的各項準備工作，在慎終如始做好鐵路站車疫情防控工作的同時，有序恢復鐵路運輸服務。<br />\n<br />\n該負責人指，4月8日解除離漢離鄂通道管控措施後，湖北省內的首趟始發列車是6點25分從漢口站開往荊州的 D9301次；開往湖北省外的首趟始發列車是7點06分從武漢站始發開往南寧東的 G431次。4月8日當天，將有276列旅客列車從武漢地區各站開往上海、深圳、成都、福州、南寧等地，其中武漢地區始發54列。從4月7日的車票預售情況看，4月8日預計有5.5萬餘名旅客乘坐火車離漢，其中前往珠三角地區的旅客較為集中，佔離漢旅客總量四成左右。"},{"pid":"98fd27942b1ec0fdb21f440f3c7c4045062e58b8","tid":1962342,"uid":35456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:56:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3c431469b02221490ec7126dce4a0e8a3ba275b","tid":1962342,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNqWtVe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNqWtVe.gif&h=f88d699e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb36630d18004168e90515f3542435e17209792d","tid":1962342,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:58:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f88045874990debee4f503d433b5bc761b8a3c9","tid":1962342,"uid":258649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:00:13.000Z","msg":"衝哂落黎香港，到香港0確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc7110330bded0ee4e35959a62af8041ec28100","tid":1962342,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"647683bb425ca4cf86249687afb05abdc9a7fc89","tid":1962342,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0